    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Sculptural works composed of a sunken design carved or incised into a hard and generally flat surface, most often the surface of a gemstone.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
